name: Multi-View Paizuri (very WIP)
description:
As this is pretty much an alpha any tips or feedback would be greatly appreciated.

A Lora trained on images of paizuri with multiple angles.

wights 0.8 - 1.3

recommended tags: paizuri, multiple_views, penis,

optional: multiple_girls, multiple_boys, (or specify like 4girls i think it might help but i haven't tested it much. the same applies for: multiple variations, different times).

I'm not sure if specifying the angles matters.

using a paizuri Lora may help.

currently can give okay-ish results, it seems to be able to recognize it's the same character and even sometimes makes differences. Can do something similar to "instant-loss" where it shows the girl (in this case getting ready for paizuri) in one panel and then the other is said action.

not sure what the best weights or width/height are. so far 512x768 or 768x512 seem to be working but need to do more testing.
